{"tid":2062756,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉兆佳稱北京不容35+或出手DQ 民主派警告會招致更大反抗","createTime":"2020-06-13T11:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T12:26:46.000Z","uid":165234,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"83979633b62f60ea3d80330e4451ba0437f81af2","tid":2062756,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnRoVJi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnRoVJi.png&h=0c8b341d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主派以取得過半數議席為立法會選舉目標，全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳就表示，北京不會容忍民主派取得過半數議席，揚言若主張攬炒的人仍拿到逾35席，北京必定出手。有民主派認為，劉的說法正反映在北京眼中，「權力係我嘅，就算你按遊戲規則攞到，我都唔畀你」的想法，而這只會招致社會更大的反抗。<br />\n<br />\n胡亦警告北京，若北京大舉以DQ阻止35+，只會激起社會更大、甚至可能是全方位的反抗，同時，亦向外界說明，北京根本無意兌現、遵守、履行一國兩制、《基本法》、《中英聯合聲》等國際承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200613/FWEYDXOEI2WNWYTKPREFE5MZ2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FFWEYDXOEI2WNWYTKPREFE5MZ2M%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrrzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=21c394c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FFWEYDXOEI2WNWYTKPREFE5MZ2M%2F&h=f3e09d0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200613/FWEYDXOEI2WNWYTKPREFE5MZ2M/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n手足 路就啱咗 行唔行到就睇大家決心</span>"},{"pid":"3c897cd69b798deb99aaed525d71150aabd248d9","tid":2062756,"uid":91422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a84ca78c7b4587b202ff6999e8291035fcdcbd0a","tid":2062756,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:44:22.000Z","msg":"民主？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0177b13c66e74bcda393e71c2b57372c8e8220e8","tid":2062756,"uid":254594